h=00_AYCYbhn5zOPB5wrFV9m0FZe37rvjY07DDLoETK29uGexpA&oe=672B6251"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "NITT_DigitalAssets_v05_HDvideo_1920x1080.png", "id": "942459706719818", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035433_942459710053151_7882200148446536338_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=F1m4fyeXsIMQ7kNvgGtK6zX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDFrsx_EalnpvmVz89Ch3if5Uko0udiKQjmWFCD41NHpw&oe=672B58C5"}, "display_name": "MLK: Now is the Time", "keywords": ["civil", "rights", "dream"], "long_description": "** WINNER: Audience Award: 2023 SXSW XR Experience Spotlight \n** NOMINEE: Emmy: 2023 Outstanding Emerging Media Program\n** NOMINEE: Social Impact Award: 2023 AIXR VR Awards\n\nIt\u2019s been sixty years since Dr. Martin Luther King delivered his iconic \"I Have a Dream\" speech, but the messages from that speech resonate today.  \n \n\u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d is an immersive journey that explores key themes of Dr. King's speech and highlights systemic inequities that persist in our society. Through first-person stories and interactions, \u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d drops you into a thoroughly modern interpretation of a contemporary March on Washington that will inform and inspire a new generation of activists. ", "short_description": "Dr. Martin Luther King's iconic \"I Have a Dream\" speech contains messages that still resonate today, sixty years later.  \n \n\u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d is an immersive journey that explores key themes of Dr. King's speech and highlights systemic inequities that persist in our society. Through first-person stories and interactions, \u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d drops you into a thoroughly modern interpretation of a contemporary March on Washington that will inform and inspire a new generation of activists."}]}, "developer_name": "Flight School Studio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://nowisthetime.time.com/privacy-p